    An empty implementation of the ProductDESProxyVisitor and ModuleProxyVisitor interfaces.

    This class combines the implementations of DefaultProductDESProxyVisitor and ModuleProxyVisitor. Like these classes, it forms an adapter to make it more convenient to implement visitors that do not explicitly implement all the visit methods. All the visit methods in this adapter class do nothing or call the visit method for the immediate superclass of their argument.
